extendedInfo.description: The National Association of Marriage Enhancement; NAME, is a non-profit organization with a network of churches and couples committed to biblical marriage ministry.We invite you to explore our Smartphone App where you will find extensive audio and video teaching on marriage, insight on how couples can strengthen their marriage, assistance for couples in distress, biblical marriage tips, and training manuals for Pre-marital counseling. Locate Free, Biblically based, Couple to Couple counseling by using the âcounselingâ icon to reach the NAME Counseling Center, nationally and internationally, nearest you or use the âcontactâ icon to reach our central location directly.Information for those who are interested in becoming CMS (Certified Marriage Specialists) couples, a certification process where lay couples within the local church undergo intensive biblical training to be raised up as counselors to the marriages within that church and community. Connection to our resource center, replete with CDs, DVDs, and books and curriculum by Dr. Leo and Molly Godzich, and other leading marriage specialist. Additionally, connect and interact with our blogs, facebook, and other social media outlets by using ready-made icons. General information about and how to register for our calendar of events such as the Annual International Marriage Conference, held this year in Phoenix AZ, which always offers multiple leading marriage specialists, Pastors and at least 40+ breakout sessions.
